= render 'shared/general_header', headline: 'About'
%section#about.container.content-section.text-center
	.row
		.col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
			/ %h2 About
			%p
				This is the start of a classy little eCommerce site built with the purpose of learning
				%a{:href => 'http://rubyonrails.org/'} Ruby on Rails
				and feeding my addiction to programming.
			%p
				Stay tuned - I'm very much looking forward to (finally) making this happen!
			%p
				This site is based on the StartBootstrap template called
				= succeed "." do
					%a{:href => "http://startbootstrap.com/template-overviews/grayscale/"} Grayscale
				It uses photos by
				= succeed "," do
					%a{:href => "https://unsplash.com/"} UnSplash
				and a custom Google Maps skin taken from
				= succeed "." do
					%a{:href => "http://snazzymaps.com/"} Snazzy Maps
